<P>__{(sharply)}
<D>__{you're a silly girl.}
<C>__{buttercup}
<D>__{yes, i am a silly girl, for not having seen sooner that you were nothing but a coward with a heart full of fear.}
<C>__{humperdinck}
<P>__{(close to erupting; speaks very distinctly)}
<D>__{i would not say such things if iwere you }
<C>__{buttercup}
<D>__{why not? you can't hurt me. westley and i are joined by the bonds of love. and you cannot track that. not with a thousand bloodhounds. and you cannot break it. not with a thousand swords. and when i say you are a coward, that is only because you are the slimiest weakling ever to crawl the earth.}
